{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843641755,"sessionID":"ses_2877a1afdffeGesSnlJUedLvuZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7887892c001677N9B6pSn0Y6q","messageID":"msg_d788644b80019PyrMMzOVZozKQ","sessionID":"ses_2877a1afdffeGesSnlJUedLvuZ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-31328f1d47e5438f800d2b337826c20b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create package structure and initialize controller module\n- [ ] Verify `pkg/workloadmanager/controller` directory exists\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/controller.go` - SandboxController structure and lifecycle\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_builder.go` - Sandbox CR building utilities\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/session_manager.go` - Session lifecycle management\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/entrypoint.go` - EntryPoint construction\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/utils.go` - Utility functions (random string, name generation)\n- [ ] Verify package compiles: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller`\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller` to ensure the package structure is valid\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Implement K8sClient for Sandbox operations\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/client/k8s_client.go` - Kubernetes client for Sandbox operations\n- [ ] Define K8sClient struct\n  - [ ] `clientset *clientset.Clientset` - Kubernetes clientset\n  - [ ] `dynamic.Interface` - Dynamic client for unstructured resources\n- [ ] Implement `GetAgentRuntime(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)`\n  - [ ] Fetch runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1 AgentRuntime resource\n  - [ ] Return error if not found\n- [ ] Implement `GetCodeInterpreter(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)`\n  - [ ] Fetch runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1 CodeInterpreter resource\n  - [ ] Return error if not found\n- [ ] Implement `CreateSandbox(ctx context.Context, namespace string, sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)`\n  - [ ] Create agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1 Sandbox resource\n  - [ ] Return created resource or error\n- [ ] Implement `DeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string) error`\n  - [ ] Delete Sandbox resource\n  - [ ] Return error if fails\n- [ ] Implement `GetPodIP(ctx context.Context, sandboxName, namespace string, sandbox *unstructured.Unstructured) (string, error)`\n  - [ ] Try direct sandboxName lookup\n  - [ ] Try Sandbox annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`\n  - [ ] Try label selector for Pod owned by Sandbox\n  - [ ] Return Pod IP or error\n- [ ] Create `k8s_client_test.go` with unit tests\n  - [ ] Test GetAgentRuntime with valid and invalid resources\n  - [ ] Test GetCodeInterpreter with valid and invalid resources\n  - [ ] Test CreateSandbox creation\n  - [ ] Test DeleteSandbox deletion\n  - [ ] Test GetPodIP with various strategies\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/client -run TestK8sClient` to verify K8sClient tests pass\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Define API types and internal types\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/api/types.go` - API request/response types\n- [ ] Define CreateSandboxRequest struct\n  - [ ] `Name string` - Workload name\n  - [ ] `Namespace string` - Kubernetes namespace\n  - [ ] `Kind string` - Resource kind (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter)\n- [ ] Define CreateSandboxResponse struct\n  - [ ] `SessionID string` - Unique session ID\n  - [ ] `SandboxID string` - Sandbox UID\n  - [ ] `SandboxName string` - Sandbox resource name\n  - [ ] `EntryPoints []EntryPoint` - List of entry points\n  - [ ] `CreatedAt time.Time` - Creation timestamp\n  - [ ] `ExpiresAt time.Time` - Expiration timestamp\n- [ ] Define GetSessionResponse struct\n  - [ ] `SessionID string`\n  - [ ] `SandboxID string`\n  - [ ] `SandboxName string`\n  - [ ] `Kind string`\n  - [ ] `Namespace string`\n  - [ ] `Name string`\n  - [ ] `EntryPoints []EntryPoint`\n  - [ ] `LastActivity time.Time`\n  - [ ] `CreatedAt time.Time`\n  - [ ] `ExpiresAt time.Time`\n  - [ ] `PodIP string`\n- [ ] Define DeleteSessionResponse struct\n  - [ ] `SessionID string`\n  - [ ] `DeletedAt time.Time`\n- [ ] Define EntryPoint struct\n  - [ ] `Protocol string` - HTTP/TCP\n  - [ ] `Endpoint string` - IP:Port\n  - [ ] `Path string` - Path prefix\n  - [ ] `Port int64` - Port number\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types/types.go` - Internal types\n- [ ] Define SandboxInfo struct\n  - [ ] `SessionID string`\n  - [ ] `SandboxID string`\n  - [ ] `SandboxName string`\n  - [ ] `WorkloadName string`\n  - [ ] `Namespace string`\n  - [ ] `Kind string` - AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\n  - [ ] `Status string` - pending/running/deleted\n  - [ ] `PodIP string`\n  - [ ] `EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint`\n  - [ ] `CreatedAt time.Time`\n  - [ ] `ExpiresAt time.Time`\n  - [ ] `LastActivity time.Time`\n- [ ] Define SandboxEntryPoint struct\n  - [ ] `Protocol string`\n  - [ ] `Endpoint string`\n  - [ ] `Path string`\n  - [ ] `Port int64`\n- [ ] Define constants for kinds\n  - [ ] `AgentRuntimeKind = \"AgentRuntime\"`\n  - [ ] `CodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"`\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/api` and `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/types` to ensure types compile\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Implement utility functions\n- [ ] Implement `RandString(n int) string` in `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/utils.go`\n  - [ ] Use charset \"abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789\"\n  - [ ] Generate n random characters\n  - [ ] Return random string\n- [ ] Implement `generateSandboxName(workloadName string) string`\n  - [ ] Use format \"{workloadName}-{random8}\"\n  - [ ] Call RandString(8) for random suffix\n  - [ ] Return sandbox name\n