, workloadName, namespace string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)` in `sandbox_builder.go`\n  - [ ] Create unstructured.Unstructured for agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1 Sandbox\n  - [ ] Set metadata.name to sandboxName\n  - [ ] Set metadata.namespace to namespace\n  - [ ] Set labels:\n    - [ ] `managed-by: agentcube`\n    - [ ] `session-id: {sessionID}`\n    - [ ] `workload-name: {workloadName}`\n    - [ ] `sandbox-name: {sandboxName}`\n  - [ ] Set annotations:\n    - [ ] `idle-timeout: \"15m\"`\n  - [ ] Set spec.replicas from AgentRuntime spec\n  - [ ] Set spec.lifecycle.shutdownTime to 8 hours from now\n  - [ ] Set spec.podTemplate from AgentRuntime spec.podTemplate\n  - [ ] Set spec.ports from AgentRuntime spec.ports\n  - [ ] Return Sandbox CR or error\n- [ ] Create `sandbox_builder_test.go` with unit tests\n  - [ ] Test Sandbox CR creation with valid AgentRuntime\n  - [ ] Test labels are set correctly\n  - [ ] Test annotations are set correctly\n  - [ ] Test spec fields are mapped correctly\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller -run TestAgentRuntimeSandboxBuilder` to verify tests pass\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Implement CodeInterpreter Sandbox CR builder\n- [ ] Implement `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(codeInterpreter *unstructured.Unstructured, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)` in `sandbox_builder.go`\n  - [ ] Create unstructured.Unstructured for agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1 Sandbox\n  - [ ] Set metadata.name to sandboxName\n  - [ ] Set metadata.namespace to namespace\n  - [ ] Set labels (same as AgentRuntime)\n  - [ ] Set annotations:\n    - [ ] `idle-timeout: \"15m\"`\n  - [ ] Set spec.replicas from CodeInterpreter spec (default 1)\n  - [ ] Set spec.lifecycle.shutdownTime to 8 hours from now\n  - [ ] Build spec.podTemplate from CodeInterpreter spec\n    - [ ] Extract container image (default: \"python:3.11-slim\")\n    - [ ] Extract container resources\n    - [ ] Extract container en